body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting us. My name is Eric Robinson and I'm from Safe Rides Car Dealership. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Janice. Can you please provide me with your date of birth? It's for our records.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is one nine nine zero, November eighteenth.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Janice. Also, could you give me the last four digits of your phone number for verification?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, the last four digits are seven eight nine zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing that information. If you have any concerns or questions, feel free to let me know.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling a bit nervous about my privacy. Can you reassure me about the security of my personal information?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Absolutely, Janice. Your privacy is important to us, and we have strict measures in place to protect your data. Is there anything specific you're worried about?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you for explaining that. I feel better now. I appreciate your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Janice. Thank you for reaching out and sharing your concerns. If you need anything else, don't hesitate to contact us. Have a great day!
